{"word":"μερίζω","slug":"μερίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μερίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μερίς'><el>μερίς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to divide, distribute</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <el>μερίζεσθαί τι</el> <i>to divide among themselves</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> rei, <i>to take part in</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be divided</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to be reckoned as part</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}